Synopsis:
   ban [#channel] <nick|nick!user@host>

Description:
   This commands adds new ban to a channel.  If no channel is specified,
   current will be used.

   The ban can be given as full hostmask, e.g. *!*@*kirjasto.jamsa.fi,
   or as nick so the hostmask will be determined by using USERHOST.

See Also:
   unban(9); mode(1)

